snippet.description:

#NewSong2025 #NewHindiSong #RomanticSong #EmraanHashmi #YamiGautam #EmraanYami #HindiSong #HindiNewSong #NewRomanticSong #NewHindiSong2025 #EmraanHashmiNewSong #YamiGautamNewSong #RomanticSongHindi #HindiSong2025 #BetaabDil #SaritDutta

“Betaab Dil” is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, “Betaab Dil” will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

🎧 Experience “Betaab Dil” — A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

👉 Don’t forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more soulful music.

Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWj7oD9SuDcGciiBQT9BQuw?sub_confirmation=1
__________________________________________________

Song Credits
Song : Betaab Dil
Singer : Sarit Dutta
Music Composer : Sarit Dutta
Lyrics : Dr Uma Naveen Mehta
Backing Vocals : Subhajit Das
Music Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sarit Dutta @ Rivertone Studio
__________________________________________________

Lyrics:-

Hum chahe itna hi 
Ab tera saath ho
Kya tune kabhi ye jana
Kitna dard hai mujhko

Bekhudi mein chal pade hai
Khudko hi ab mitane
Mere kadam rukte nahi 
Teri galiyon me aane se

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Baaton ne teri
Mujhko saari raat jagaya
Sanson ne teri
Mujhko yu apna banaya

Koi lamha nahi hai mera
Jisme tu nazar na aaya
Na hamne koi khata ki
fir kyu tune di hai saja

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

snippet.title: Shri Ram Chandra Kripalu - Extended Version | Abhay Jodhpurkar | Ram Bhajan | Ram Stuti
snippet.description:
श्री रामचंद्र कृपालु भजन का यह विस्तारित संस्करण अभय जोधपुरकर की मधुर आवाज़ में राम भक्ति का अनमोल अनुभव कराता है। यह भजन प्रभु श्री राम की करुणा, शक्ति और मर्यादा का स्मरण कराता है और मन को शांति एवं भक्ति से भर देता है।

ईश्वर के ऐसे अनेक मधुर प्यारे भजन, मंत्र आरतियां सुनने के लिए सब्सक्राइब करें : https://www.youtube.com/SaregamaBhakti

Audio Credits:-

Artist: Abhay Jodhpurkar
Music: Mohit Musik
Lyrics: Traditional

Lyrics:

श्री रामचन्द्र कृपालु भजुमन
हरण भवभय दारुणं ।
नव कंज लोचन कंज मुख
कर कंज पद कंजारुणं ॥१॥

कन्दर्प अगणित अमित छवि
नव नील नीरद सुन्दरं ।
पटपीत मानहुँ तडित रुचि शुचि
नोमि जनक सुतावरं ॥२॥

भजु दीनबन्धु दिनेश दानव
दैत्य वंश निकन्दनं ।
रघुनन्द आनन्द कन्द कोशल
चन्द दशरथ नन्दनं ॥३॥

शिर मुकुट कुंडल तिलक
चारु उदारु अङ्ग विभूषणं ।
आजानु भुज शर चाप धर
संग्राम जित खरदूषणं ॥४॥

इति वदति तुलसीदास शंकर
शेष मुनि मन रंजनं ।
मम् हृदय कंज निवास कुरु
कामादि खलदल गंजनं ॥५॥

मन जाहि राच्यो मिलहि सो
वर सहज सुन्दर सांवरो ।
करुणा निधान सुजान शील
स्नेह जानत रावरो ॥६॥

एहि भांति गौरी असीस सुन सिय
सहित हिय हरषित अली।
तुलसी भवानिहि पूजी पुनि-पुनि
मुदित मन मन्दिर चली ॥७॥

snippet.title: ekō - Malayalam Movie| Official Teaser| Sandeep Pradeep|Dinjith Ayyathan| Mujeeb Majeed|Bahul Ramesh
snippet.description:
Presenting the official teaser of ekō, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ekō marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence — exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.
